name: Lucifer's Exile
description:
Imagine having it all, in exchange for looking the other way in the face of injustice. Lucifer, the bringer of light, always wanted to free humans from God. Who do you think taught humans fire? Why did he want to give Eve knowledge? Who welcomed the first woman, who refused to submit to Adam and was expelled from paradise?

Lucifer dared to contradict God's words, to stand up to injustice, sacrificing all that was his world.
